CLASS z2ui5_cl_util_range DEFINITION
  FINAL CREATE PUBLIC.
  PUBLIC SECTION.

    CONSTANTS:
      BEGIN OF signs,
        including TYPE string VALUE `I`,
        excluding TYPE string VALUE `E`,
      END OF signs.

    CONSTANTS:
      BEGIN OF options,
        equal                TYPE string VALUE `EQ`,
        not_equal            TYPE string VALUE `NE`,
        between              TYPE string VALUE `BT`,
